I"‡<ol>
  <li>Generate <a href="/debian-ssl-snakeoil-certificate/"><em>Snakeoil SSL Certificate</em></a> â€“ or:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>openssl req <span class="nt">-x509</span> <span class="nt">-newkey</span> rsa:4096 <span class="nt">-nodes</span> <span class="nt">-sha256</span> <span class="nt">-keyout</span> /etc/ssl/private/ssl-cert-snakeoil.key <span class="nt">-out</span> /etc/ssl/certs/ssl-cert-snakeoil.pem <span class="nt">-days</span> 3650 <span class="nt">-subj</span> <span class="s2">"/CN=&lt;</span><span class="nv">$PUBLIC_IP_ADDRESS</span><span class="s2">&gt;"</span>
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Create <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/nginx/sites-enabled/000-default.conf</code>:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>server {
  listen 80 default_server;
  listen 443 ssl default_server;
  server_name _;

  ssl_certificate /etc/ssl/certs/ssl-cert-snakeoil.pem;
  ssl_certificate_key /etc/ssl/private/ssl-cert-snakeoil.key;

  return 444;
}
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

